  "visual": {
    "visualType": "textbox",
    "objects": {
      "general": [
        {
          "properties": {
            "paragraphs": [
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Daily = all-day deduplicated total (HOUR 25) · Hourly = sum of hours 00–23 · Inflation = Hourly ÷ Daily. Use Daily for all reporting; Hourly is validation only. (* = source columns for the OTS / PaS / Total Population KPIs.)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " • "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Additive events — Inflation ≈ 1.00.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " Signals, Ext Signals, Ext Signals 2. Observation events, so the all-day total equals the sum of the hours by construction; Daily and Hourly are interchangeable."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " • "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Unique-person counts — Inflation > 1 (median ≈ 1.5).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " Users, * Extrapolated_number_of_users (PaS), * Extrapolated_users_2 (Total Population). The all-day figure deduplicates people; summing hours re-counts repeat visitors. Use Daily — the index measures repeat-visit overcount."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " • "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Reach / eye-contact counts — Inflation < 1 (median ≈ 0.7–0.9).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " Eye Contacts, Eye Contacts Weighted, Impressions Weighted / Weighted 2, * Extrapolated_number_of_eye_contacts (OTS). Extrapolated to population — each hour scaled to its own smaller population while the all-day row is scaled to the full daily population, so the hours don't sum to the day. Use Daily; the hourly sum understates reach, not a real drop."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " • "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Dwell Time — Inflation < 1 (median ≈ 0.71).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " An average (%), not a count — it can't be summed; the ratio just compares all-day vs hourly average."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " "
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Bottom line:",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " real overcount appears only for unique-person counts (Users, PaS, Total Population). For additive events the index is trivially 1; for reach metrics it reflects the extrapolation method, not an audience change."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
